synopsis.text: Kingdom s are in peril and a hidden garden holds the key to salvation as Nozomi Yumehara and her Pretty Cure team embark on a new adventure. Summoned once more by the enigmatic Flora, the girls must locate her in the elusive Cure Rosegarden, a place accessible only with the magical Rose Pact and the combined powers of the four kings of the lands neighboring Palmier. As the sinister organization Eternal seeks to infiltrate the garden and steal the Rose Pact, the Pretty Cure must rely on newfound allies: Syrup, a delivery boy with the extraordinary ability to transform into a giant bird, and the captivating Milky Rose, a formidable warrior with a mysterious past. Together, they must protect the true essence of the world and uncover the secrets of the Cure Rosegarden.
